<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Georg Zenger zu Rosenberg</head><p>Der Rat versichert erneut die Freundschaft mit Friedrich von Kemnat, Oheim des Adressaten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_143" id="70v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_143_r2l15">Görgen ʒenger ʒu <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_143_r2l16"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe eẅch <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> eẅr Öheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l17">brıef ʒaıgt hab . dıe wır Jm vnd er vns geſchrıben <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd </del> darauf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l18">Jr begert daʒ wır eẅch von ſeinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> oder Jm ein ſıcherheıt <expan>anſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l19">etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dem <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒwyr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l20"><expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Daʒ wir noch ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt Jm niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>ſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l22">
<add><ab facs="#facs_143_r1l1"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn </ab></add> guts / vnd daʒ wır niht <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . wer dıe <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / als Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_143_r2l21">das vnd anders </ab></add> ın <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>brıef<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l23">wol mugt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / alſo ſchreıben wır das <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> auch daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l24">wır mıt <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> noch ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l25"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l26"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> margarete </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_143" id="70v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Görgen Zenger zu <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wie ewch
                                <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan>, ewr öheim, brief zaigt hab, die wir im und
                        er uns geschriben <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darauf ir begert, daz wir
                        ewch von seinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> oder im ein sicherheit
                                <expan>anschreibe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir dem <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> zwyr <expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        daz wir noch zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit im niht
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, denn</add> guts, und daz wir niht
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, wer die
                            <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, als ir <add>das und anders</add> in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>brief<ex>en</ex></expan> wol mugt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also schreiben wir das
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> auch, daz wir mit
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> noch zu disen
                            <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Margarete.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
